{"tid":2219983,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解女士m到有M巾 男士夢遺無夢遺巾？","createTime":"2020-09-27T09:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T14:45:23.000Z","uid":51346,"like":104,"dislike":611,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7c703e1d9f6a5e1c1acf2020e55276cc9eafec","tid":2219983,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:38:25.000Z","msg":"夢遺完up住成晚都會對jj唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女士每個月用m巾最多咪10日<br />\n<br />\n但男士每次瞓覺都有機會夢遺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n瞓晏覺一次 夜晚一次 再乘30日 即係60次<br />\n<br />\n根本商機無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講打得多飛機就唔會夢遺 <br />\n<br />\n想像力豐富根本打幾多飛機都會發春夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通真係要用m巾頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過相信好多巴絲同我一樣身懷巨龍 著住m巾瞓會好焗促<br />\n<br />\n應該得安睡褲比較適合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnaz5mO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqnaz5mO.jpg&h=aafae5db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好入正題 <br />\n以上講嘅都係治標唔治本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我發明咗呢樣嘢幫各位巴絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKoBzfz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKoBzfz.jpg&h=46567488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似個名講咁 用咗佢就唔會再夢遺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用家示意圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nbO9Pp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nbO9Pp.jpg&h=d8eccf33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅色帶固定雙腳 黃色杯左右再有支架固定住用家同張床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25FMb3O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25FMb3O.jpg&h=f5c1d41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅色路線為夢遺後精液嘅走向<br />\n<br />\n射出嚟之後會撞頂 然後順住流線型嘅杯身流返入龜頭 <br />\n（杯身已搽滿消炎藥 防止精液倒流引起發炎）<br />\n<br />\n用耐咗之後 精液多次嘅彈出彈入相信會引發身體嘅學習機能 發春夢都唔會再射精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加埋上個post講嘅精子進化論 喺出面見過世面嘅精子 衣錦還鄉之後會同初出茅蘆嘅後生精分享經驗 就算再夢遺都會q手起人牆 唔出精 <br />\n費事白行一趟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都要keep住打丁 唔係我怕會爆袋而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90150e5cbe838bbbb4c073f4e0dc89a0518d8c59","tid":2219983,"uid":51346,"like":79,"dislike":18,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"尷尬囉"},{"pid":"134456a909727d8c1e338bbe4a54f0ca3c52f22a","tid":2219983,"uid":350634,"like":58,"dislike":4,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"飛機杯咪係囉"},{"pid":"88f49783bc1cd2db4f106d5d0fb8ce6599222064","tid":2219983,"uid":20820,"like":136,"dislike":3,"score":133,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"戴 condom訓覺咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者打多啲就唔洗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e40294f46e6b21edef1b250019823d42e2dfb6b","tid":2219983,"uid":350634,"like":90,"dislike":4,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"90150e5cbe838bbbb4c073f4e0dc89a0518d8c59","tid":2219983,"uid":51346,"like":79,"dislike":18,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"尷尬囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:40:02.000Z","msg":"屌 自己秒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2aa6e6257cfcded4e1cf11870fa3f729a44c70","tid":2219983,"uid":334765,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"瞓前塞定條巨龍入飛機杯咪解決到個問題"},{"pid":"3d8bd039bfa161a888fcebd9a28b771fea0c2556","tid":2219983,"uid":51346,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"134456a909727d8c1e338bbe